CodedHospitalAdmissionCmsVariableDataMart

The Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services (CMS) coded hospital admission variable data mart contains variables used by CMS to calculate expected value metrics. Each row represents a master coded hospital admission encounter. The variables that are defined by a list of Condition Category (CC) codes are using CC version 22.
